reviews.title: GoodReads Review of Griftopia: Bubble Machines, Vampire Squids, and the Long Con That Is Breaking America: Rating - 5/5
reviews.content: Taibbi's Griftopia is a book terrifying in it's scope and revelation of reality. Few journalists have been able to grasp the financial crisis and what its systematic abuses and lack of consequences means for America. Taibbi, however, has his finger right on the rotting heart of American economics.
